hopobject.body: What part of do you come from? vitex 225 mg No sooner had I said “backup van,” than Chris had talked me out of it. Always trust the guide. Within 20 minutes the sun was out and we were breezing through a cottage-speckled idyll among wild ponies, peacocks and more blackberry hedges. And the terrain was flat as a tack. Next morning, over coffee on the terrace at Terra Vina hotel, I put Cycle Tours’ promise to provide ‘as much or as little cycling as you like’ to the test.
